\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 The rest of this description goes into the weeds. Sorry, but this is a complex system, built in a new way that AI enables. The good news is, the rest of this document is optional. You\'92ve already read the good stuff. Here\'92s the bullets:\
\
\'97 A system cheap enough to deliver an ROI almost immediately.\
\
\'97 Maintains the comfort level of your home when there is someone there to enjoy it while still reducing your energy bills. \
\
\'97 Can be expanded into an advanced security system and wildfire mitigation system without replacing equipment you\'92ve already bought. \
